  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8dc419c3ab2c2280740bdc93fe3f11e2.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a twist of fate, our heroes learn of a safe haven ark. Their journey ends at its gates, only to be shunned—King Chipmunk has reserved every spot on the upper deck! What a jerk. Amidst a crowd of seatless creatures, there’s but one option left: dethrone the tyrant chipmunk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/254ea9e8c9427879cecc40a00fd8f4ee.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play at your own pace through async multiplayer! Chill out in Arena Mode and battle against user-generated teams to earn 10 Victories. Want to test your skills? Climb the leaderboard in Rapture Mode and utilize powerful Buff Cards to build an overpowered squad while battling endless waves of teams. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/0993c6c514728c46a7553865823fe4de.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The flood is coming. Only the Ark will save them. That is… unless the evil King Chipmunk reserves all the seats! Fight for your own salvation and hone your skills in a complete single-player campaign filled with hand-drawn cutscenes and art. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/3ec48d1c3f19315b8138db894d2768e4.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and customize a massive variety of silly and adorable animals ranging across the animal kingdom. Bearbarians, Catsassins, Samurai Shibas, and… Hamster Weebs? Learn their strengths, weaknesses, and synergies to assemble your team.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8dc419c3ab2c2280740bdc93fe3f11e2.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a twist of fate, our heroes learn of a safe haven ark. Their journey ends at its gates, only to be shunned—King Chipmunk has reserved every spot on the upper deck! What a jerk. Amidst a crowd of seatless creatures, there’s but one option left: dethrone the tyrant chipmunk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/254ea9e8c9427879cecc40a00fd8f4ee.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play at your own pace through async multiplayer! Chill out in Arena Mode and battle against user-generated teams to earn 10 Victories. Want to test your skills? Climb the leaderboard in Rapture Mode and utilize powerful Buff Cards to build an overpowered squad while battling endless waves of teams. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/0993c6c514728c46a7553865823fe4de.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The flood is coming. Only the Ark will save them. That is… unless the evil King Chipmunk reserves all the seats! Fight for your own salvation and hone your skills in a complete single-player campaign filled with hand-drawn cutscenes and art. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/3ec48d1c3f19315b8138db894d2768e4.avif?t=1762957880\" width=616 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and customize a massive variety of silly and adorable animals ranging across the animal kingdom. Bearbarians, Catsassins, Samurai Shibas, and… Hamster Weebs? Learn their strengths, weaknesses, and synergies to assemble your team.</p>",
